structure.unit: PUBLIC PRINTING AND DISTRIBUTION OF PUBLIC DOCUMENTS

law.history: Repealed 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 176, sec. 16. -- Amended 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 26, sec. 1. -- Amended 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 136, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 3953a-2, 3953a-3.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Duties of Superintendent of Public Printing; contracts for work not covered by regular contracts; qualification to perform work; bond of printer.
